data.title: George Bush Library and Museum
data.text:
Memcons and Telcons

Below, please find a list of memcons (memoranda of face-to-face conversation) and telcons (memoranda of telephone conversation) between President George Bush and world leaders. Selecting dates with an active link will bring you to a pdf of the document. Assume that President Bush and one or more of his advisors are participating in the meeting/call unless otherwise specified in the document.

Please contact the Bush Library Archives for information on mandatory review procedures to request the release of exempted information withheld in partially released or denied documents.

You can sort the table as needed by clicking on the table column headers.
